<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Informix cuts EPS view.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Informix cuts EPS view.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Everen Securities Inc analyst William Lanzon said Wednesday he reduced his earnings estimates for Informix Corp to a loss of $0.39 a share from a profit of $0.88 for 1997 and to a profit of $0.35 a share from a profit of $1.17 for 1998.</p>
<p>-- On April 1, Informix said it expected a substantial operating loss and net loss for the first quarter because of a revenue shortfall.</p>
<p>-- Lanzon said he continues to rate Informix a near-term market performer and a long-term outperformer.</p>
<p>-- Informix shares were off 31/32 at 8-15/32.</p>
<p>((Reuters Chicago Newsdesk (312) 408-8787))</p>
